{"tid":1534754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔係話不割蓆？","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T06:24:07.000Z","uid":38165,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"21919cfe013c27cb9f96341db2aa96adcba9dbb5","tid":1534754,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:05:36.000Z","msg":"我本身都唔想開依個post<br />\n琴日毛EE好撚大聲咁講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n近排咁多人話和理非乜乜乜<br />\n勇武乜乜乜<br />\n唔係和勇不分<br />\n只有手足咩？<br />\n<br />\n係一毛帶風向？定香港人變？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重申一次<br />\n香港人 不割蓆！！<br />\n咪再話和理非 勇武 手足<br />\n大家各有各做 <br />\n唔好迫人做任何野<br />\n齊上齊落</span></span>"},{"pid":"73a82fbe9c15d3270f4199985a1e86f978987a0a","tid":1534754,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:05:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a4cc274b5a1a56e739f968ba8ae56ff26123328","tid":1534754,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:06:07.000Z","msg":"不割蓆請正皮。我係明呃正皮 吹咩？咬我食？"},{"pid":"dd20a5842d839a85828de064c491e344d07582c6","tid":1534754,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:06:21.000Z","msg":"不割蓆"},{"pid":"6628719f06f174d8fdf2e2a35734ac2093ce3978","tid":1534754,"uid":76745,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:07:15.000Z","msg":"屌佢地係想佢地進步 唔好再咁多道德枷鎖<br />\n失敗唔係因為人數唔夠 而係被道德枷鎖鎖死自己"},{"pid":"b561201672455dc1b0c195e2a1bcf0b5cc2e86d1","tid":1534754,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:10:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"208deaa45540f10d6d08856b82cd2b9f65808a0c","tid":1534754,"uid":117232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:13:07.000Z","msg":"有時好佩服藍絲<br />\n人地非禮 老強 爆眼 斬人 打爆小學生都唔割<br />\n仲要作野幫黑警<br />\n<br />\n黃絲還手、火魔法、塞鐵塞機、打玻璃、打左膠 樣樣割到仆街"},{"pid":"c56c6f94ce88100d82104c2f1a676048578c6721","tid":1534754,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"208deaa45540f10d6d08856b82cd2b9f65808a0c","tid":1534754,"uid":117232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:13:07.000Z","msg":"有時好佩服藍絲<br />\n人地非禮 老強 爆眼 斬人 打爆小學生都唔割<br />\n仲要作野幫黑警<br />\n<br />\n黃絲還手、火魔法、塞鐵塞機、打玻璃、打左膠 樣樣割到仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:20:33.000Z","msg":"藍屍就係不割蓆既極致 <br />\n手足都好大進步架啦<br />\n已經無乜人對汽油彈 打狗 打爆港鐵 反感<br />\n反而覺得果班人係應得<br />\n好次我老母咁<br />\n佢以前都係和理非 好抗拒暴力<br />\n而家佢會話 打得好 死都唔撚可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3409785e2a13044ad4ae1b1f7367f954f75d3aa7","tid":1534754,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好再屌手足 有乜事都可以慢慢講 唔好迫人做任何野 好多野迫唔到 各有各做啦"},{"pid":"d8db82baf07595893e1973127356db6d5f30d443","tid":1534754,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"殺狗都唔撚割呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 